msgid ""
"Integrate Society Speaks programmatically. Power your embeds, snapshots, and"
" editorial insights with JSON APIs built for newsroom workflows and "
"developer velocity."
msgstr ""
"Society Speaks को प्रोग्राम्स रूप से इंटीग्रेट करें। JSON APIs के साथ अपने "
