msgstr "2. कोई निर्भरता आवश्यक नहीं है"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:278
msgid ""
"Uses Node's built-in <code class=\"bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded text-"
"gray-800\">fetch</code> (Node 18+) and <code class=\"bg-gray-100 px-1 "
"rounded text-gray-800\">crypto</code>. No <code class=\"bg-gray-100 px-1 "
"rounded text-gray-800\">npm install</code> needed."
msgstr ""
"Node के अंतर्निहित <code class=\"bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded text-"
"gray-800\">fetch</code> (Node 18+) और <code class=\"bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded"
" text-gray-800\">crypto</code> का उपयोग करता है। कोई <code class=\"bg-"
"gray-100 px-1 rounded text-gray-800\">npm install</code> आवश्यक नहीं है।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:339
msgid ""
"We use these words consistently in the Partner Portal, API responses, and "
"support materials — skim this once and the rest of the docs stay "
"predictable."
msgstr ""
"हम Partner Portal, API responses, और support materials में इन शब्दों का "
"सुसंगत तरीके से उपयोग करते हैं — इसे एक बार देख लें और बाकी docs "
"पूर्वानुमानित रहते हैं।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:344
msgid ""
"The umbrella for one reader-facing voting experience: headline title, how it"
" anchors to your site (<code>article_url</code> and/or "
"<code>external_id</code>), partner environment (test/live), one "
"embed/consensus URLs, and the combined participation underneath it. Creating"
" a discussion via API establishes this container first."
msgstr ""
"एक पाठक-सामना करने वाले voting experience के लिए छाता: headline title, यह "
"आपकी साइट से कैसे जुड़ता है (<code>article_url</code> और/या "
"<code>external_id</code>), partner environment (test/live), एक "
"embed/consensus URLs, और इसके तहत combined participation। API के माध्यम से "
"discussion बनाने से पहले यह container स्थापित होता है।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:348
msgid ""
"Individual prompts inside that umbrella — each collects its own agree / "
"disagree / unsure counts. Populate them during creation with "
"<code>seed_statements</code> or an <code>excerpt</code> that fuels AI seeds;"
" add/edit them afterward in the portal; optionally allow anonymous readers "
"to propose more when embed submissions are toggled on for that discussion."
msgstr ""
"उस छाते के अंदर व्यक्तिगत prompts — प्रत्येक अपनी own agree / disagree / "
"unsure counts एकत्र करता है। इन्हें <code>seed_statements</code> के साथ "
"creation के दौरान populate करें या <code>excerpt</code> provide करें जो AI "
"seeds को fuel करे; बाद में portal में इन्हें add/edit करें; optionally "
"anonymous readers को अधिक propose करने की अनुमति दें जब embed submissions उस"
" discussion के लिए toggled हों।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:357
msgid ""
"The usual pattern is “one discussion per published URL,” but that is a "
"choice, not a requirement. You can create discussions for article pages, "
"attach a CMS id without a public article, or mix both so reporting stays "
"consistent across your stack."
msgstr ""
"सामान्य pattern है \"एक discussion प्रत्येक published URL के लिए,\" लेकिन यह"
" एक choice है, requirement नहीं। आप article pages के लिए discussions बना "
"सकते हैं, एक CMS id attach कर सकते हैं public article के बिना, या दोनों को "
"mix कर सकते हैं ताकि reporting आपके stack में सुसंगत रहे।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:358
msgid ""
"Regardless of identifiers, remember the split: lookup/create returns "
"<code>discussion_id</code>; statements are modeled separately and surfaced "
"through the embed, portal statement tools, and snapshot payloads."
msgstr ""
"identifiers की परवाह किए बिना, split को याद रखें: lookup/create "
"<code>discussion_id</code> return करता है; statements को अलग से model किया "
"जाता है और embed, portal statement tools, और snapshot payloads के माध्यम से "
"surfaced होते हैं।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:361
msgid "Programmatic embed (recommended)"
msgstr "प्रोग्रामेटिक embed (अनुशंसित)"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:363
msgid "1) Lookup discussion by article URL"
msgstr "1) लेख URL द्वारा चर्चा खोजें"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:364
msgid ""
"2) If none exists, create the discussion shell (seed statements optionally "
"in the same call)"
msgstr ""
"2) यदि कोई मौजूद नहीं है, तो discussion shell बनाएँ (optionally seed "
"statements उसी call में)"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:365
msgid ""
"3) Store <code>discussion_id</code> and use <code>embed_url</code>; review "
"statements inside the portal if you need tweaks"
msgstr ""
"3) <code>discussion_id</code> store करें और <code>embed_url</code> use करें;"
" यदि आपको tweaks की ज़रूरत हो तो portal में statements review करें"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:381
msgid "Manual embed (quick start)"
msgstr "मैनुअल embed (त्वरित शुरुआत)"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:383
msgid ""
"Use the Embed Generator to create one-off iframes. It relies on the same "
"APIs and returns the same <code>discussion_id</code> and "
"<code>embed_url</code>."
msgstr ""
"एकबारी iframes बनाने के लिए Embed Generator का उपयोग करें। यह समान APIs पर "
"निर्भर करता है और समान <code>discussion_id</code> और <code>embed_url</code> "
"लौटाता है।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:387 app/templates/partner/hub.html:410
msgid "Open embed generator"
msgstr "embed जेनरेटर खोलें"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:397
msgid ""
"Editors and producers can skim the section below; share the engineering "
"notes with IT."
msgstr ""
"Editors और producers नीचे दिए गए section को skim कर सकते हैं; IT के साथ "
"engineering notes share करें।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:400
msgid "For editorial & product teams"
msgstr "Editorial & product teams के लिए"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:402
msgid ""
"Vocabulary cheat sheet: one <strong>discussion</strong> = one voting topic "
"plus its embed wrapper; several <strong>statements</strong> sit underneath —"
" the lines readers answer with agree / disagree / unsure."
msgstr ""
"Vocabulary cheat sheet: एक <strong>discussion</strong> = एक voting topic "
"plus its embed wrapper; कई <strong>statements</strong> नीचे बैठते हैं — वे "
"lines जिनमें पाठक agree / disagree / unsure के साथ उत्तर देते हैं।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:402
msgid "Longer explanation →"
msgstr "लंबी व्याख्या →"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:403
msgid ""
"You decide what each voting topic is called and what readers see first — "
"article tie-in is optional; live blogs, hubs, and special projects can use a"
" stable id instead of a story URL."
msgstr ""
"आप decide करते हैं कि प्रत्येक voting topic को क्या कहा जाए और पाठक पहले "
"क्या देखें — article tie-in optional है; live blogs, hubs, और special "
"projects एक stable id का उपयोग कर सकते हैं story URL के बजाय।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:404
msgid ""
"Every web address where the snippet might load must be approved in your "
"Partner Portal — rehearsal sites and live sites are separate."
msgstr ""
"हर web address जहाँ snippet load हो सकता है, वह Partner Portal में approved "
"होना चाहिए — रिहर्सल sites और live sites अलग हैं।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:405
msgid ""
"If your readers type both <code>www.</code> and bare domain names, register "
"<strong>two</strong> approvals."
msgstr ""
"यदि आपके पाठक दोनों <code>www.</code> और bare domain names type करते हैं, तो"
" <strong>दो</strong> approvals register करें।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:406
msgid ""
"Ask engineering to add the short tracking tag (<code>?ref=…</code>) so "
"reports stay attributable."
msgstr ""
"Engineering से short tracking tag (<code>?ref=…</code>) add करने के लिए कहें"
" ताकि reports attributable रहें।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:406
msgid "What the tags mean →"
msgstr "Tags का अर्थ क्या है →"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:407
msgid ""
"Optional: ask for automatic height on the box so long articles do not clip "
"(one small script on your side)."
msgstr ""
"Optional: automatic height के लिए पूछें ताकि लंबे articles को clip न किया "
"जाए (आपकी ओर से एक छोटी script)।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:407
msgid "How it works →"
msgstr "यह कैसे काम करता है →"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:408
msgid ""
"Prefer automatic “something changed” pings to your systems over manual "
"checking."
msgstr ""
"Manual checking के बजाय automatic \"something changed\" pings को अपने "
"systems को prefer करें।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:408
msgid "Webhooks overview →"
msgstr "Webhooks overview →"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:412
msgid "For engineering & hosting"
msgstr "Engineering & hosting के लिए"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:414
msgid ""
"Match test API keys only with rehearsal domains; live keys only with "
"verified production domains."
msgstr ""
"परीक्षण API keys को केवल रिहर्सल domains के साथ match करें; live keys केवल "
"verified production domains के साथ।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:415
msgid ""
"Rehearsal (<code>test</code>) embeds in production always need a resolvable "
"parent page from the browser — even without "
"<code>PARTNER_EMBED_REQUIRE_PARENT_ORIGIN</code>."
msgstr ""
"Rehearsal (<code>test</code>) embeds production में हमेशा को एक resolvable "
"parent page की ज़रूरत होती है browser से — "
"<code>PARTNER_EMBED_REQUIRE_PARENT_ORIGIN</code> के बिना भी।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:416
msgid ""
"Optional hardening env: "
"<code>PARTNER_EMBED_REQUIRE_PARENT_ORIGIN=true</code> (production, live "
"partner embeds only) blocks iframe HTML when we cannot resolve a parent page"
" from <code>Origin</code> or <code>Referer</code> — stricter, and may affect"
" uncommon browsers or privacy settings."
msgstr ""
"Optional hardening env: "
"<code>PARTNER_EMBED_REQUIRE_PARENT_ORIGIN=true</code> (production, live "
"partner embeds only) iframe HTML को block करता है जब हम parent page को "
"<code>Origin</code> या <code>Referer</code> से resolve नहीं कर सकते — "
"stricter, और uncommon browsers या privacy settings को प्रभावित कर सकता है।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:417
msgid ""
"Inline reader submissions from the embed honour "
"<code>EMBED_STATEMENT_SUBMIT_RATE_LIMIT_ACTOR</code> and "
"<code>EMBED_STATEMENT_SUBMIT_RATE_LIMIT_IP</code> in configuration (plus "
"per-person limits)."
msgstr ""
"Embed से inline reader submissions "
"<code>EMBED_STATEMENT_SUBMIT_RATE_LIMIT_ACTOR</code> और "
"<code>EMBED_STATEMENT_SUBMIT_RATE_LIMIT_IP</code> को configuration में "
"honour करते हैं (plus per-person limits)।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:426
msgid ""
"Find a discussion by the URL of your article. The lookup returns discussion "
"metadata (<code>discussion_id</code>, <code>embed_url</code>, etc.); the "
"statements readers vote on arrive with that discussion’s embed and snapshot "
"payloads."
msgstr ""
"अपने article के URL से एक discussion खोजें। Lookup discussion metadata "
"return करता है (<code>discussion_id</code>, <code>embed_url</code>, आदि); "
"statements जिन पर पाठक vote करते हैं वह उस discussion के embed और snapshot "
"payloads के साथ आते हैं।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:437
#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:768
msgid "Query Parameters"
msgstr "क्वेरी पैरामीटर"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:442
#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:548
#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:773
#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:850
#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:855
#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:878
