msgstr "लेख URL (URL-एन्कोडित)"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:447
#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:778
#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:783
#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:788
