msgstr "Attribution के लिए आपका publication का नाम"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:899
msgid ""
"Allow inline reader submissions in embed for this discussion (default false)"
msgstr ""
"इस discussion के लिए embed में inline reader submissions की अनुमति दें "
