#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:903
msgid ""
"Notes: Provide at least one identifier (<code>article_url</code> or "
"<code>external_id</code>) and either <code>excerpt</code> or "
"<code>seed_statements</code>."
msgstr ""
"Notes: कम से कम एक identifier (<code>article_url</code> या "
"<code>external_id</code>) और <code>excerpt</code> या "
"<code>seed_statements</code> दोनों में से कोई एक provide करें।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:904
msgid ""
"Recommendation: keep <code>embed_statement_submissions_enabled</code> as "
"<code>false</code> for most article pages, and enable it only for "
"discussions where your team wants inline statement intake from the embed."
msgstr ""
"Recommendation: अधिकांश article pages के लिए "
"<code>embed_statement_submissions_enabled</code> को <code>false</code> रखें,"
" और इसे केवल उन discussions के लिए enable करें जहां आपकी टीम embed से inline"
" statement intake चाहती है।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:965
msgid "Success Response (201)"
msgstr "Success Response (201)"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:990
msgid "<code>invalid_api_key</code> - Missing or invalid API key"
msgstr "<code>invalid_api_key</code> - Missing or invalid API key"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:994
msgid ""
"<code>missing_identifier</code> or <code>missing_content</code> - Need "
"(article_url or external_id) and excerpt/seed_statements"
msgstr ""
"<code>missing_identifier</code> या <code>missing_content</code> - "
"(article_url या external_id) और excerpt/seed_statements की जरूरत है"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:998
msgid "<code>discussion_exists</code> - Discussion already exists for URL"
msgstr ""
"<code>discussion_exists</code> - URL के लिए discussion पहले से मौजूद है"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1008
msgid "Update discussion policy (Authenticated)"
msgstr "Discussion policy को update करें (Authenticated)"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1010
msgid ""
"Use this to close/reopen discussions, toggle integrity mode, and control "
"inline embed submissions."
msgstr ""
"Discussions को close/reopen करने, integrity mode को toggle करने, और inline "
"embed submissions को control करने के लिए इसका use करें।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1024
msgid ""
"Recommended default for most article pages: "
"<code>\"embed_statement_submissions_enabled\": false</code>. Enable "
"<code>true</code> for selected high-engagement discussions (for example, "
"live blogs or campaign hubs)."
msgstr ""
"अधिकांश article pages के लिए recommended default: "
"<code>\"embed_statement_submissions_enabled\": false</code>। Selected high-"
"engagement discussions के लिए <code>true</code> enable करें (उदाहरण के लिए, "
"live blogs या campaign hubs)।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1030
msgid "Webhook callbacks (Authenticated)"
msgstr "Webhook callbacks (Authenticated)"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1031
msgid ""
"Configure signed lifecycle callbacks to avoid polling. Use server-to-server "
"calls with a portal-issued key."
msgstr ""
"Polling से बचने के लिए signed lifecycle callbacks configure करें। Portal-"
"issued key के साथ server-to-server calls का use करें।"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1033
