msgstr ""
"<code class=\"text-purple-700\">PATCH "
"/api/partner/webhooks/{endpoint_id}</code> - pause/resume करें और event "
"subscriptions को update करें"

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1036
#, python-brace-format
